<p>The kitchen is also easy on the eyes with white cabinets and gray counters with a washed brick covering for the double oven. A farmer's sink with modern fixtures also stands out as well as a tucked-in microwave.</p>

<p>Sleep here: The master bedroom is roomy and even has an area for a reading nook with plenty of windows for natural light</p>

